data.description: Awesome 5 bedroom 2 1/2 bath Colonial in sought after East Pittsford Manor! This one boasts a bright and spacious formal dining room and living room, fireplaced family room and a first-floor laundry! The upstairs has five bedrooms with hardwood floors and two full baths! Slate entry foyer awaits your arrival. Square footage of 2,256 was measured by agent. PRICE REDUCED!! So much house for the money! Perfect for large or growing family. Great backyard.
